




{"id":16566,"date":"2025-08-11T17:10:48","date_gmt":"2025-08-11T10:10:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=16566"},"modified":"2025-08-11T17:19:05","modified_gmt":"2025-08-11T10:19:05","slug":"vi-sao-nen-chon-tivi-chuyen-dung-thay-vi-tivi-gia-dinh-cho-lop-hoc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/vi-sao-nen-chon-tivi-chuyen-dung-thay-vi-tivi-gia-dinh-cho-lop-hoc\/","title":{"rendered":"V\u00cc SAO N\u00caN CH\u1eccN TIVI CHUY\u00caN D\u1ee4NG THAY V\u00cc TIVI GIA \u0110\u00ccNH CHO L\u1edaP H\u1eccC?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trong xu th\u1ebf gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n nay, vi\u1ec7c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb trong gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp. Tivi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb quan tr\u1ecdng, gi\u00fap truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i n\u1ed9i dung tr\u1ef1c quan, sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat h\u1ecdc sinh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i tivi n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc. Nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc v\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tivi gia \u0111\u00ecnh do gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh r\u1ebb h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho kh\u00f4ng gian l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 ho\u1eb7c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e8n s\u00e1ng, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfu l\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p. Tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb l\u1edbp k\u00ednh ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00f3i v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ch\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1, gi\u00fap h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh lu\u00f4n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0o. \u0110\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi tivi gia \u0111\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ecdi h\u1ecdc sinh, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ng\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i l\u1edbp, \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u00ecn r\u00f5 n\u1ed9i dung. Ngo\u00e0i ra, k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng theo ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-16580 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/0-800x800-4084-1.webp\" alt=\"V\u00cc SAO N\u00caN CH\u1eccN TIVI CHUY\u00caN D\u1ee4NG THAY V\u00cc TIVI GIA \u0110\u00ccNH CHO L\u1edaP H\u1eccC?\" width=\"900\" height=\"680\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/0-800x800-4084-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/0-800x800-4084-1-529x400.webp 529w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/0-800x800-4084-1-768x580.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/0-800x800-4084-1-600x453.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t cao, c\u00f3 khi t\u1eeb s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ec1u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, 5 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 ng\u00e0y\/tu\u1ea7n. Tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn, linh ki\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng m\u1ea1ch \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, cho tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u1eeb 50.000 gi\u1edd tr\u1edf l\u00ean. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, tivi gia \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho v\u00e0i gi\u1edd xem m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c s\u1ebd d\u1eabn t\u1edbi n\u00f3ng m\u00e1y, gi\u1ea3m tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd b\u00f3ng LED v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed g\u00e2y hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u \u1ea3nh ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea3nh sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-16567 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2261_tivi_lg_55qned80tsa_7_org-3.webp\" alt=\"V\u00cc SAO N\u00caN CH\u1eccN TIVI CHUY\u00caN D\u1ee4NG THAY V\u00cc TIVI GIA \u0110\u00ccNH CHO L\u1edaP H\u1eccC?\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2261_tivi_lg_55qned80tsa_7_org-3.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2261_tivi_lg_55qned80tsa_7_org-3-600x400.webp 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2261_tivi_lg_55qned80tsa_7_org-3-768x512.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng cung c\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u chu\u1ea9n k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i h\u01a1n, t\u1eeb HDMI, USB,Type C, t\u1edbi c\u00e1c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y gi\u00fap gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu n\u1ed9i dung t\u1eeb laptop, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu v\u1eadt th\u1ec3. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u00f2n t\u00edch h\u1ee3p OPS, cho ph\u00e9p bi\u1ebfn m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u00e1y t\u00ednh ch\u1ea1y Windows ho\u1eb7c Android, thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, tivi gia \u0111\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o t\u00ednh n\u0103ng gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, khi\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c t\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u00e0o h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-16570 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/TIVI_INNOSMART-1-1.webp\" alt=\"V\u00cc SAO N\u00caN CH\u1eccN TIVI CHUY\u00caN D\u1ee4NG THAY V\u00cc TIVI GIA \u0110\u00ccNH CHO L\u1edaP H\u1eccC?\" width=\"900\" height=\"808\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/TIVI_INNOSMART-1-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/TIVI_INNOSMART-1-1-446x400.webp 446w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/TIVI_INNOSMART-1-1-891x800.webp 891w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/TIVI_INNOSMART-1-1-768x689.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/TIVI_INNOSMART-1-1-600x539.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 r\u00f5 h\u01a1n, tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh su\u1ed1t bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc. Nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng khi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 qu\u00e9t cao gi\u00fap h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y m\u1ecfi m\u1eaft. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng khi tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu video gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, th\u00ed nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng 3D. Tivi gia \u0111\u00ecnh, khi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb n\u00f3ng, gi\u1ea3m hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb v\u00e0 g\u00e2y gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-16585 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/khoac-ao-moi-cho-truong-tieu-hoc-du-hang-1.webp\" alt=\"V\u00cc SAO N\u00caN CH\u1eccN TIVI CHUY\u00caN D\u1ee4NG THAY V\u00cc TIVI GIA \u0110\u00ccNH CHO L\u1edaP H\u1eccC?\" width=\"900\" height=\"540\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/khoac-ao-moi-cho-truong-tieu-hoc-du-hang-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/khoac-ao-moi-cho-truong-tieu-hoc-du-hang-1-667x400.webp 667w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/khoac-ao-moi-cho-truong-tieu-hoc-du-hang-1-768x461.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/khoac-ao-moi-cho-truong-tieu-hoc-du-hang-1-600x360.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">An to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 l\u1edbp k\u00ednh c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ee7i ro v\u1ee1 khi b\u1ecb va ch\u1ea1m, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi d\u1ec5 v\u1ec7 sinh v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ng b\u1ee5i. Nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn an to\u00e0n cho m\u1eaft, gi\u1ea3m \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh, gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc sinh khi nh\u00ecn m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. Tivi gia \u0111\u00ecnh hi\u1ebfm khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y, do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ri\u00eang cho m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1edd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y tr\u1ef1c quan, v\u1eeba mang l\u1ea1i t\u00ednh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cao v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, th\u00ec c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc. INNOSMART cung c\u1ea5p d\u00f2ng tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i cao, k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111a d\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb 55 inch \u0111\u1ebfn 110 inch, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1ecfng g\u1ecdn, d\u1ec5 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p m\u1ecdi kh\u00f4ng gian l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, ch\u1ed1ng l\u00f3a: C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ch\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh quan s\u00e1t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf m\u1ecdi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i linh ho\u1ea1t: T\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ngo\u1ea1i vi kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9: V\u1eadn h\u00e0nh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1edd m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n kh\u1eaft khe c\u1ee7a gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T\u00edch h\u1ee3p ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y: Hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c n\u1ed9i dung \u0111a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u00c2m thanh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao: Loa t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u00e2m thanh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho c\u1ea3 l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc sinh: L\u1ecdc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5p nh\u00e1y, gi\u1ea3m m\u1ecfi m\u1eaft khi h\u1ecdc l\u00e2u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">D\u1ec5 b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p: Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf module th\u00f4ng minh gi\u00fap thay th\u1ebf, n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p linh ki\u1ec7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/post-Vi-sao-nen-chon-tivi-chuyen-dung-thay-vi-tivi-gia-dinh-cho-lop-hoc-2.webp\" alt=\"V\u00cc SAO N\u00caN CH\u1eccN TIVI CHUY\u00caN D\u1ee4NG THAY V\u00cc TIVI GIA \u0110\u00ccNH CHO L\u1edaP H\u1eccC?\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">V\u1edbi INNOSMART, l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean tr\u1ef1c quan, sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">FAQ \u2013 C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/span><\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec so v\u1edbi tivi gia \u0111\u00ecnh?<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u2192 Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb r\u00f5 trong \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1ea1nh, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y; tivi gia \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> V\u00ec sao tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng b\u1ec1n h\u01a1n khi d\u00f9ng trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc?<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u2192 Linh ki\u1ec7n ch\u1ecbu t\u1ea3i cao, \u00edt h\u1ecfng h\u00f3c khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1edd m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c?<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u2192 \u0110\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng cao, g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn r\u1ed9ng, r\u00f5 n\u00e9t \u1edf m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> Tivi chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng c\u00f3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u2192 C\u00f3, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> D\u00f9ng tivi gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y?<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u2192 C\u00f3, d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y m\u1ecfi m\u1eaft, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh k\u00e9m r\u00f5, gi\u1ea3m t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c khi d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong xu th\u1ebf gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n nay, vi\u1ec7c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb trong gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp. Tivi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb quan tr\u1ecdng, gi\u00fap truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i n\u1ed9i dung tr\u1ef1c quan, sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat h\u1ecdc sinh. Tuy&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":16569,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-16566","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16566","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=16566"}],"version-history":[{"count":14,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16566\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":16587,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16566\/revisions\/16587"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16569"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=16566"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":